      <title>厄瓜多尔火灾威胁富裕社区，迫使总统回家</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/ecuador-fires-threaten-rich-neighborhoods-force-president-home</link>
      <description><![CDATA[基多的富裕社区仍然面临火灾威胁，在消防员与厄瓜多尔首都的森林大火搏斗之际，学校已转为在线教学，直至本周末。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/ecuador-fires-threaten-rich-neighborhoods-force-president-home</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 25 Sep 2024 19:31:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>经济放缓担忧加剧 澳大利亚财政部长访问中国</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/australia-s-treasurer-heads-to-china-as-fears-grow-over-slowdown</link>
      <description><![CDATA[澳大利亚财政部长吉姆·查尔默斯将于周四开始访华，这是该国最高经济决策者七年来首次访华，而堪培拉方面越来越担心其最大贸易伙伴中国经济放缓可能带来的影响。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/australia-s-treasurer-heads-to-china-as-fears-grow-over-slowdown</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 25 Sep 2024 19:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>法国极右翼寻求废除马克龙的关键养老金法</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/france-s-far-right-seeks-to-abolish-macron-s-key-pension-law</link>
      <description><![CDATA[玛丽娜·勒庞领导的极右翼政党正在公开向埃马纽埃尔·马克龙的新政府施加更大压力，试图推翻法国总统不受欢迎的养老金改革。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/france-s-far-right-seeks-to-abolish-macron-s-key-pension-law</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 25 Sep 2024 18:16:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>意大利表示不会对公司额外利润征税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/italy-says-it-won-t-seek-to-impose-tax-on-extra-company-profits</link>
      <description><![CDATA[意大利将寻求通过银行和企业的直接出资来为国家预算提供资金的方法，但不会对企业的额外利润征税。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/italy-says-it-won-t-seek-to-impose-tax-on-extra-company-profits</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 25 Sep 2024 18:10:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普呼吁苹果解密刺客手机</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/trump-calls-on-apple-to-decrypt-phones-of-would-be-assassins</link>
      <description><![CDATA[共和党总统候选人唐纳德·特朗普呼吁苹果公司协助联邦调查人员获取两名被控密谋暗杀他的男子的手机和应用程序。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/trump-calls-on-apple-to-decrypt-phones-of-would-be-assassins</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 25 Sep 2024 17:41:52 GMT</pubDate>
